705
00:28:03,360 --> 00:28:04,720
but you can't shake it.

706
00:28:05,560 --> 00:28:07,064
And your interest is a strange

707
00:28:07,106 --> 00:28:09,274
thing because it comes upon you.

708
00:28:09,600 --> 00:28:11,440
It makes itself manifest.

709
00:28:11,485 --> 00:28:13,153
It's not something that you create.

710
00:28:13,194 --> 00:28:14,404
You can squelch it.

711
00:28:14,760 --> 00:28:16,120
You can fail to follow it.

712
00:28:16,489 --> 00:28:17,720
But it's very difficult

713
00:28:17,745 --> 00:28:19,366
to elicit it if it's not there.

714
00:28:19,396 --> 00:28:21,280
I had a client, for example, who, he

715
00:28:22,520 --> 00:28:24,280
was with a woman that he really—she

716
00:28:24,680 --> 00:28:27,055
was a good friend of his, but there was no

717
00:28:27,080 --> 00:28:29,249
sexual chemistry as far as he was concerned.

718
00:28:29,291 --> 00:28:30,542
And he really liked her,

719
00:28:30,584 --> 00:28:32,752
and he had gone out with a number of women

720
00:28:32,794 --> 00:28:34,440
who he had plenty of sexual chemistry

721
00:28:34,465 --> 00:28:38,175
