722
00:28:38,200 --> 00:28:41,295
So he was happy that he was with someone that he

723
00:28:41,320 --> 00:28:43,815
liked, but he couldn't get that spark going.

724
00:28:43,840 --> 00:28:45,775
And no matter how hard he tried,

725
00:28:45,800 --> 00:28:46,681
that didn't happen.

726
00:28:46,722 --> 00:28:48,682
And the reason I'm telling you that is because

727
00:28:48,724 --> 00:28:51,320
you see that interest has a certain autonomy.

728
00:28:52,600 --> 00:28:54,215
It's something that calls to you.

729
00:28:54,240 --> 00:28:55,646
It's an old idea that people

730
00:28:55,688 --> 00:28:57,055
have a calling or a destiny.

731
00:28:57,080 --> 00:28:59,525
And one of the things I've done in my podcast,

732
00:28:59,560 --> 00:29:01,100
I get to talk to people who've

733
00:29:01,400 --> 00:29:03,695
had various levels of accomplishment.

734
00:29:03,800 --> 00:29:06,455
I'm always interested in how they got interested

735
00:29:06,480 --> 00:29:08,735
in what they got interested in,

736
00:29:08,760 --> 00:29:10,290
because something gripped them

737
00:29:10,320 --> 00:29:12,880
with enough force that they followed and

738
00:29:13,119 --> 00:29:14,735
became disciplined, and then

739
00:29:14,760 --> 00:29:16,720
that turned into success, right?

740
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:19,415
OK, so you find something that's interesting to

741
00:29:19,440 --> 00:29:22,043
you, it calls to you, and then you can establish,

742
00:29:22,335 --> 00:29:23,840
what, a relationship with it?

743
00:29:24,360 --> 00:29:26,562
Is that the right way of thinking about it?

744
00:29:26,589 --> 00:29:27,173
Likely.

745
00:29:27,214 --> 00:29:28,424
So what happens to Moses is

746
00:29:28,465 --> 00:29:31,000
that he starts investigating this.

747
00:29:31,025 --> 00:29:32,594
He gets closer and closer to it.

748
00:29:32,636 --> 00:29:34,304
Imagine you're interested in something;

749
00:29:34,345 --> 00:29:35,847
now you start to investigate it.

750
00:29:35,888 --> 00:29:37,775
So now you're getting closer to it.

751
00:29:37,800 --> 00:29:39,433
And as you get closer to it, it deepens.

752
00:29:39,475 --> 00:29:41,268
You know that if you have an intellectual,

753
00:29:41,309 --> 00:29:42,310
artistic interest.

754
00:29:42,440 --> 00:29:44,562
The more you study it, the deeper it gets.

755
00:29:44,600 --> 00:29:46,080
It starts to spread out,

756
00:29:46,105 --> 00:29:48,015
so it covers more and more territory,

757
00:29:48,040 --> 00:29:50,360
and it gets deeper, whatever that means.

758
00:29:50,960 --> 00:29:52,040
What does deeper mean?

759
00:29:52,840 --> 00:29:54,840
It means you get closer to the basics,

760
00:29:55,160 --> 00:29:56,895
you get closer to the foundation.

761
00:29:56,920 --> 00:29:58,640
You get closer to the assumptions.

762
00:29:59,160 --> 00:30:01,410
If you start to get to know someone deeply,

763
00:30:01,440 --> 00:30:03,453
you understand their deepest motivations,

764
00:30:03,480 --> 00:30:05,015
the pattern of their motivation

765
00:30:05,040 --> 00:30:06,660
all the way down to the root.

766
00:30:06,960 --> 00:30:09,440
You go down the levels to go deeper.

767
00:30:09,640 --> 00:30:11,460
Well, that's what happens when Moses

768
00:30:11,880 --> 00:30:14,800
starts to approach this burning bush.

769
00:30:14,879 --> 00:30:16,320
He realizes he's starting

770
00:30:16,345 --> 00:30:18,215
to tread on sacred ground.

771
00:30:19,480 --> 00:30:21,255
So he takes off his shoes,

772
00:30:21,280 --> 00:30:23,219
and then he continues his investigation.

773
00:30:23,261 --> 00:30:25,815
That's a gesture of humility,

774
00:30:25,840 --> 00:30:28,920
to take off your shoes in that context.

775
00:30:29,266 --> 00:30:31,393
OK, so now you're pursuing something that's

776
00:30:31,435 --> 00:30:32,686
interesting to you,

777
00:30:32,720 --> 00:30:35,200
and you allow that to change you as you pursue it.

778
00:30:35,354 --> 00:30:36,815
And you do that in humility,

779
00:30:36,840 --> 00:30:39,080
assuming that if you pursue this interest

780
00:30:39,760 --> 00:30:42,640
